column2: and it and the water came with a little carafe on your table.  This is nice because I drink a lot of each.  The green eggs were delicious. They were very flavorful and I would totally get them again.  My toast was only half toasted
column3: and the potatoes were super fried.  The apple wood smoked chicken sausage (or something like that) was really good and not at all heavy.
